x10g - GTK application for controlling X10 devices.

Features:
* Currently, application supports CM11A controller
  with serial port interface (USB-to-serial converters
  are of course supported too).

* On/off, light dimming and time synchronization are
  supported.

Installation:
$ cd x10g
$ make
$ ./x10g

Make sure that you are running application as user which have
access to serial port(s) - in particular, port, where X10 controller
is connected.
